name: Cat Cafe
summary: Step into Cat Cafe, a highly immersive VR experience filled with adorable feline companions and endless possibilities. With a fully physics-based animation system, our virtual cats exhibit realistic behaviors and interactions, responding dynamically to your every action. Each cat has its own distinct personality traits, such as being playful, shy, affectionate, or mischievous, and autonomously selects behaviors based on their current state, traits, and your interactions.
